<Date>Mon Nov 12 00:00:00 CST 2007
<Content>I really like the small size and easy to use features of this player. The USB port charging is extremely convenient since you can recharge it on any computer without worrying about carrying the cord with you all the time. Copying music onto it is easy. The FM radio is a nice feature when you cant decide what music to listen to. Its very lightweight so easy to bring with you everywhere. The MicroSD slot means you can add more music easily. I wasnt impressed with the original earphones, but once I changed them, the sound was much better.   
